    <h1>Prompt Chaining</h1>
    <p class="description">A prompt engineering technique that breaks complex AI tasks into <strong>sequential steps</strong> — where each output feeds the next — to produce higher-quality results than a single monolithic prompt ever could.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
